'''爱思唯尔''' （{{lang-nl|Elsevier}}，{{IPA-nl|ˈɛlzəviːr}}）是一家[[信息|信息]]和{{link-en|解析|Analytics}}公司和世界上[[科学|科学]]、[[技术|技术]]和[[医学|医学]]信息的主要提供者之一。爱思唯尔作为[[出版|出版]]公司成立于1880年<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.adobe.com/content/dam/acom/en/marketing-cloud/campaign-management/pdfs/adobe-campaign-customer-story-elsevier.pdf|title=Elsevier finds its one globe voice|accessdate=2018-08-05|archive-date=2016-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821134327/https://www.adobe.com/content/dam/acom/en/marketing-cloud/campaign-management/pdfs/adobe-campaign-customer-story-elsevier.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，现在是[[RELX集團|励讯集团]]（RELX Group，2015年前名为Reed Elsevier）的一部分<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.Relx.com|title=RELX Group homepage|accessdate=|date=|last=Reller|first=Tom|publisher=|website=|archive-date=2018-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711181833/http://www.relx.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其产品包括《[[柳葉刀_(雜誌)|柳叶刀]]》、《[[四面体_(期刊)|四面体]]》和《[[細胞_(期刊)|细胞]]》等[[学术期刊|学术期刊]]，[[ScienceDirect|ScienceDirect]]电子期刊集，{{link-en|趋势 (期刊)|Trends (journals)|“趋势”（Trends）系列}}和{{link-en|新见 (期刊)|Current Opinion (Elsevier)|“新见”（Current Opinion）系列}}期刊，在线引文[[数据库|数据库]][[斯高帕斯数据库|斯高帕斯（Scopus）]]和{{link-en|ClinicalKey|}}临床医生解决方案。 爱思唯尔的产品和服务覆盖整个[[学术研究|学术研究]][[產品生命週期管理_(市場)|生命周期]]，包括[[软件|软件]]和数据管理、教导和评估工具。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://scholarlykitchen.sspnet.org/2017/02/02/plum-goes-orange-elsevier-acquires-plum-analytics/|title=Plum Goes Orange – Elsevier Acquires Plum Analytics|accessdate=2018-08-05|archive-date=2018-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805203647/https://scholarlykitchen.sspnet.org/2017/02/02/plum-goes-orange-elsevier-acquires-plum-analytics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[File:Reed_Elsevier_Logo.svg|替代=Reed Elsevier（爱思唯尔前身）的标志]]前身）的标志]]爱思唯尔每年在2,500份期刊上出版超过430,000篇文章。<ref name="RELX 2017 Report">{{Cite web |url = http://www.relx.com/~/media/Files/R/RELX-Group/documents/reports/annual-reports/relx2017-annual-report.pdf |title = 2017 RELX Group Annual Report |date = 2018-03 |accessdate =  |website = RELX Group Company Reports |publisher = 励讯集团 |archive-date = 2018-06-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180613140348/http://www.relx.com/~/media/Files/R/RELX-Group/documents/reports/annual-reports/relx2017-annual-report.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>其档案包含超过13万份文件和30,000本电子书籍。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/|title = Science Direct|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = Reller|first = Tom|archive-date = 2018-05-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180511125310/https://www.sciencedirect.com/|dead-url = no}}</ref>每年下载总量超过900万次。<ref name="RELX 2017 Report" />

