g their research|accessdate=2017-03-26|archive-date=2016-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161119234726/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-switch/wp/2013/12/19/how-one-publisher-is-stopping-academics-from-sharing-their-research/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

